										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>A marketing proposal is more than just a plan of action. Itâ€™s a piece of marketing collateral in and of itself and has direct influence over whether the client chooses you or a competitor.</p>
<p>In this complete guide, Iâ€™m going to equip you with everything you need (including templates!) to create a marketing proposal that will impress your prospects, earn their trust, distinguish you from competitors, and win the signature.</p>
<p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/marketing-proposal-example.webp" alt="how to write a marketing proposal - example of designed marketing proposal" width="936" height="540" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-78439" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/marketing-proposal-example.webp 936w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/marketing-proposal-example-480x277.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 936px, 100vw" /></p>
