<h3>5. Jotformâ€™s esignature marketing proposal builder</h3>
<p>Jotform is an esignature platform with a WSWYG design editor. With <a href="https://www.jotform.com/sign/232595865746069" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Jotfromâ€™s marketing proposal template</a>, the core content is already in place, you just have to fill in the blanks. You can also make changes to the master template and customze the design to your branding. In addition, you can use Jotform itself to share the proposal via email and collect e-signatures from any device. It doesnâ€™t include examples and itâ€™s pretty basic, so this is best for marketers who know what makes an effective proposal and just need a tool to make it look great and/or offer esigning.</p>
