<h2>Start winning more clients with these marketing proposal templates</h2>
<p>As I said, a marketing proposal is a piece of marketing collateral in and of itself. And itâ€™s part art, part science. With the right balance of information and metrics with design and delivery, a good proposal can win over the client and set the stage for a successful project.</p>
