<p>Believe it or not, your brand messaging can even shine through in your live chat instances. The small B2B software business, HipLink, is a great example of this with its chatbot prompts that use promotional language. This brand messaging example focuses on two main value propositions and uses an overall friendly tone.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/brand-messaging-example-live-chat.jpg" alt="brand messaging - example of brand messaging in live chat" width="537" height="634" class="aligncenter wp-image-76903 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/brand-messaging-example-live-chat.jpg 537w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/brand-messaging-example-live-chat-480x567.jpg 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) 537px, 100vw" /></p>
