		<title>How to Use HARO for Backlinks &#038; PR (with a Free Pitch Template)</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2023/02/28/how-to-use-haro-for-backlinks</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Guest Author]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Tue, 28 Feb 2023 13:00:58 +0000</pubDate>
